<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-561-189  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 561 189.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>EDGE: Work-Group Computing Report  Oct 22 1990 v1 n22 p4(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT EDGE Publishing 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Word processing: Volkswriter is back with a new family of wordprocessing software. (product announcement)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Volkswriter Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Volkswriter 2 (Word processing software) (Product introduction)Volkswriter 4 (Word processing software) (Product introduction)Volkswriter 6 (Word processing software) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Word Processing SoftwareProduct IntroductionUpgrading.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Volkswriter Inc., is back.andP;  The producers of word processing software for theIBM PC, Monday introduced a new family of fully compatible word processors,Volkswriter 2, 4, and 6.andM;The company's upgrade policy offers users a path to move from any of thepackages to any other, for considerably less than the cost of a new program.andM;Volkswriter 2,4, and 6 share a common user interface, including identicalkeystroke commands.andP;  Users can &quot;jump&quot; up and down the product line withoutany relearning or retraining.andP;  Users within the same organization who havedifferent word processing needs can use compatible software and share files.andM;The new family offers innovative features including multilingualcapabilities, Grammatik IV, and automatic recognition of file formats.andP;  Inaddition, Volkswriter 2, 4, and 6 are LAN installable.andM;VOLKSWRITER 2, 4, 6 FEATURES Volkswriter 2, 4, and 6 offer increasinglysophisticated features as the user moves up the product line.andM;VOLKSWRITER 2:  FOR ENTRY-LEVEL USERS - BASIC WP PROGRAMandM;-- 170,000-word spelling checkerandM;-- Mail mergeandM;-- Auto-hyphenationandM;-- Extensive printer supportandM;VOLKSWRITER 4, RELEASE 2.0:  FOR EXECUTIVE USERS CONTAINS ALL OF THE FEATURESIN VOLKSWRITER 2, PLUS:andM;-- Integrated Grammatik IVandM;-- Integrated 310,000-word thesaurusandM;-- Extensive font supportandM;-- Page preview and macrosandM;VOLKSWRITER 6:  FOR POWER USERS CONTAINS ALL OF THE FEATURES IN VOLKSWRITER4, PLUS:andM;-- Personal publishing capabilitiesandM;-- Inset Graphics Technology for importing, processing, andandM;printing desktop publishing graphicsandM;-- Integrated HP AutoFont support and integrated AGFAandM;Compugraphics' Intellifont scaling technologyandM;-- Comprehensive font support and managementandM;OPTIONAL ADD-ON MODULES Volkswriter also offers add-on modules that can beused with any product in the family, and continue to work when the user movesup or down the product line.andP;  Add-ons include:andM;-- LAN installation kitsandM;-- &quot;Volks Word for Word,&quot; Volkswriter's file conversion packageandM;which converts to and from 30 word processing formatsandM;-- Extended 610,000-word thesaurusandM;-- Grammatik IV (for Volkswriter 2)andM;-- Computer, legal, and medical dictionaries (separately or bundledandM;together)andM;-- Multilingual modules allow languages to be intermixed:andM;-- Dictionaries for spelling and auto-hyphenation in Australian,andM;British, Danish, Dutch, French, German, Italian, Norwegian,andM;Spanish, and SwedishandM;-- Thesauruses in the same languages as above, except Danish,andM;Dutch, and SwedishandM;-- Definition dictionaries in American, Australian, and BritishandM;PRICING AND AVAILABILITY Volkswriter 4 will be available in late fall of1990, and will retail for $249.andP;  Volkswriter 2 will be available in the firstquarter of 1991 and will retail for $149.andP;  Volkswriter 6 will be availablesecond quarter 1991 and will retail for $499.andP;  Current Volkswriter customerscan upgrade to the new Volkswriter 2, 4, and 6 at discounted prices.andM;Key Executive: Vicky L. Boddie, president of Volkswriter Inc.andO;</TEXT></DOC>